{"id":"da-001","text":"他拿起电话打给了母亲。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-002","text":"孩子们在院子里打球。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-003","text":"雨点轻轻地打在窗户上。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-004","text":"她每天清晨都去公园打太极拳。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-005","text":"请帮我打印两份会议材料。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-006","text":"爷爷从井里打了一桶水。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-007","text":"工匠正在为新房打家具。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-008","text":"出门前别忘了打扫房间。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-009","text":"他们坐在树下打牌聊天。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-010","text":"医生建议他去医院打针。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-011","text":"妹妹正在学习打毛衣。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-012","text":"比赛结束后双方打成了平手。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-013","text":"他在门口打了一辆出租车。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-014","text":"大家打算周末一起去郊游。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-015","text":"这家小店晚上九点打烊。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-016","text":"他打开书本认真读了起来。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-017","text":"请在表格里打一个勾。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-018","text":"战士们在山脚下搭起帐篷打夜。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-019","text":"小猫打了一个长长的哈欠。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-020","text":"运动员正在操场上打拳。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-021","text":"这件事打乱了我们原来的计划。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-022","text":"清晨的钟声打破了山村的寂静。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-023","text":"父亲在院墙上打了一个孔。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-024","text":"她给远方的朋友打了一封电报。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-025","text":"渔民天不亮就出海打鱼。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-026","text":"哥哥周末常和同学打篮球。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-027","text":"我先去车站打听末班车的时间。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-028","text":"灯光把他的影子打在墙上。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-029","text":"他们打包好行李准备出发。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-030","text":"请不要随意打断别人的发言。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-031","text":"这场胜利大大打动了现场观众。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-032","text":"母亲把鸡蛋打进碗里搅匀。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-033","text":"工人给木箱打上了编号。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-034","text":"他用手电筒打了一个信号。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-035","text":"奶奶在算盘上打得又快又准。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-036","text":"老师让我们先打好写作提纲。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-037","text":"他打着雨伞走过湿漉漉的街道。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-038","text":"演员上台前仔细打扮了一番。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-039","text":"他打心眼里感谢大家的帮助。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-040","text":"我们应该及时打消他的顾虑。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-041","text":"队员们打起精神继续赶路。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-042","text":"她把丝带打成一个漂亮的结。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-043","text":"这场大雨把麦子打倒了一片。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-044","text":"朋友见面时互相打了招呼。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-045","text":"新修的公路打通了两个村庄。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-046","text":"我们要把基础打得更加牢固。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-047","text":"他打量着眼前这座古老的房子。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-048","text":"清洁工正在给地板打蜡。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-049","text":"他一早就去市场打酱油。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
{"id":"da-050","text":"风吹得窗帘不停地打转。","target_char":"打","source":"bundled_fallback","license":"public_domain","access_date":"2024-01-01","is_storable":true,"is_trainable":true,"is_publishable":false}
